metadata.name: You Made My Name Special
metadata.description:
Whispering your name like a sweet refrain.
You made me feel complete.

Repeatedly, endlessly
I vow to be there for you.

You gave significance to my existence.
My heart beats with unbridled joy.

.

This genesis piece is a culmination of my experience months ago when I first created Harmony. Every time, I strive to create works that take you back to a core memory from your past. 

To this day, I am constantly searching for ways to connect with viewers on different levels and make a profound impact on how they view AI-collaborative pieces. Combining nature and artificial intelligence has allowed me to express my mind in ways that clears the fog in my head. 

Harmony has made my name special.

.

An AI-Collaborative Piece. 
Midjourney, Photoshop, and CAD.
2400 x 3400px

-wren
